text: KVSH-LP (101.9 FM) is a radio station licensed to serve the community of Vashon, Washington. The station is owned by Voice of Vashon. It airs a community radio format. The station was assigned the call sign KVOI-LP by the Federal Communications Commission on March 3, 2014. A week later, on March 10, the station changed its call sign to KVSH-LP ==References== ==External links== * Official Website * VSH-LP VSH-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2014 Category:2014 establishments in Washington (state) Category:Community radio stations in the United States Category:King County, Washington
